204
00:16:48,879 --> 00:16:51,919
[SPEAKER_03] Ovo je način na koji trošimo novac u tim prostorima, općenito je to početak.

205
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:52,879
[SPEAKER_02] Sigurno, da.

206
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:56,159
[SPEAKER_02] Prvi put kad smo o tome razgovarali na Subclubu.

207
00:16:56,799 --> 00:16:58,720
[SPEAKER_03] Da, znam, ali to je tamo, znate.

208
00:16:58,960 --> 00:17:13,759
